<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-44-0270 </DOCNO><TEXT>The purpose of this paper is to delve into the current status of outageplanning, provide a rationale for why good planning strategies are socritical to &quot;Optimized Plant Performance&quot; and to propose a frameworkor model which could aid in moving into the 21st century in a way thatmaximizes the performance of their power plants. The utilities have madegreat strides in improving this performance, and Westinghouse is pleasedto have been involved in some of these endeavors.</TEXT></DOC>